The Cocktail Club
The Cocktail Club
Thursday, September 25th | 7pm
The riveting evening takes place in The Wilder’s Lobby Bar, where every detail has been meticulously designed to evoke a sense of old-world glamour, a stunning backdrop for this exclusive event.
An evening at The Cocktail Club includes an indulgent experience as handcrafted cocktails take center stage while renowned chefs curate a sumptuous four-course menu thoughtfully paired with each libation. Each course is expertly designed to showcase the unique flavors and nuances of both the cuisine and the libations, resulting in a truly harmonious dining experience.
